quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  19,77,"Enee, a yi'aali -an Nulaa…óo- on yeddu…óo hujjaaji Amen …óin, o yeddi Kammbaaji Amen …óin, o wi'i: "Si mi maayii, mi immintinoyaama maatun mi okkee jawdi …óuu…óundi e …ďi…ó…ďe"."
  19,78,"Enee, o anndu ko wirnii kon si o wi'i ko o wi'i kon no …ďanngiri?! Kaa o ∆īettodii e Joomi makko aadi fii yo O naadu mo Aljanna, O okkoya mo ton jawdi e …ďi…ó…ďe?!"
  19,79,"Fiyaake on wanaa no o aa∆īori non, aray Men winnda ko o woni wowlude kon e ko o woni gollude kon, Men …ďeydana mo Lepte e dow lepte makko …óen, sabu ko o nodditii kon immorde e meere nden."
  19,80,"Men Rona ko o acci kon immorde e jawdi e …ďi…ó…óo …ďaawo Men halkii mo, o ara e Amen √Ďalnde Darngal ko o weddii…óo hara o …ďooraama ko o wonunoo dakmitorde kon immorde e jawdi e jaahu."
  19,81,"Sirkoo…ďe …ďen jogitii hoore-ma…ď…ďe rewetee…ďe gaanin Alla; fii yo …ďen laatano …ďe sembinoo…ďe e walloo…ďe, …ďe foolira sabu ma…ď…ďe."
  19,82,"Fiyaake on wanaa no …ďe aa∆īori non, …óii rewetee…ói …ói …ďe rewata …óum gaanin Alla, …ói yeddoyay √Ďalnde Darngal dewal ngal sirkoo…ďe …ďen rewunoo…ói ngal, …ói wo…ó…óitoo e ma…ď…ďe, …ói laatanoo …ďe ay…ďe."
  19,83,"Enee, a yi'aali -an Nulaa…óo- wonnde Menen Men nulii Seytanuuji …óin, Men wurti…ói e dow heefer…ďe …ďen hi…ói ∆īuuna…ďe e wa…óugol geddi …óin e faddagol ka Diina Alla e ∆īuunugol."
  19,84,"Wata a he√Īor -an Nulaa…óo- …óa…ď…ďirgol Alla yaccin- gol halkugol …ďe, anndu Men limay …ďe woni nguur- ndan ma…ď…ďe …óam limugol, haa si ha…ótii dummunne nennangol …ďe Men lepta …ďe yeru ko …ďe hanndi kon."
  19,85,"JaŇčto -an Nulaa…óo- √Ďalnde Darngal, √Ďalnde Men moo…ďoyta huliroo…ďe …ďen Joomi mu'un -…óoftagol Yamiraa…ói Makko …óin e wo…ó…óitagol Ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin- ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe jamaa teddinaa…óo."
  19,86,"Men sogga heefer…ďe …ďen haa ka Jahannama ko …ďe …óon…óaa…ďe."
  19,87,"∆Āee heefer…ďe …ďe maraa tefanngol wo…ď…ďe ma…ď…ďe si wonaa on jogtaninoo…óo Alla aadi ka aduna fii gom- …óinngol Mo e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen."
  19,88,"Alyahuuda en e Annasaaraa en e wo…ď…ďe e sirkoo…ďe …ďen wi'i: " Hinnorante jogitike …ďi…ó…óo"."
  19,89,"Gom…óii on addii -ko onon wowloo…ďe …óii- huunde mawnunde."
  19,90,"Kammuuli …óin no …ďadoo seekaade immorde e ngol konngol a√Īaangol, leydi ndin no …ďadoo seekaade, pelle …óen no do'a yanude muncoo."
  19,91,"∆äum fow,ko sabu ko …ďe dammbani(askitina) kon Hinnorante …ďi…ó…óo, Alla Toowii e …óum Toowal mawngal."
  19,92,"Gasataa nde Hinnorante jogitotoo …ďi…ó…óo Senaade wonanii Mo e …óum."
  19,93,"Alaa won…óo ka kammuuli e ka leydi immorde e Malaa'ikaa…ďe …ďen e yim…ďe …ďen e jinnaaji …óin si wanaa o aroyay ka Joomi makko √Ďalnde Darngal ko o yankinii…óo."
  19,94,"Gom…óii O Hu…ďindorii …ďe Ganndal,o limibe limgol, suu…óaaki e Makko immorde e ma…ď…ďe hay e huunde."
  19,95,"Gooto kala e ma…ď…ďe aroy ka Makko √Ďalnde Darngal ko o weddii…óo hara o maraa ballo o maraa jawdi."